			<div class="dablink">This article is about acids in chemistry.  For the drug, see <a href="/wiki/Lysergic_acid_diethylamide" title="Lysergic acid diethylamide">Lysergic acid diethylamide</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Acid_(disambiguation)" title="Acid (disambiguation)">Acid (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
